Taino / Jokers:  We're willing to be as courteous and sharing as possible.  This raid for us was also scheduled back in december, will be the last raid led by our new GM Almadine until she returns to fulltime play after US Tax season is over.  We dont see ourselves backing down from this raid at all because quite frankly its our last chance to do it with Alma until April.  Has anyone mentioned that this is VC's FIRST solo plane run?  thats right, we've had lots of fun on joint planar runs in the past but this is our first time ever doing one in house.  We're pretty proud of that and excited too.  <br>
<br>
We EXPECT to have to share planes with folks.  We're glad its Agema and Jokers that we'll be sharing with.  We hope that we can keep out of each others hair, let you know when loot is rotting that we dont need and vice versa, and that everyone has a good time.<br>
<br>
If something goes wrong, please keep the above in mind.  We  all seem to be somewhat reasonable adults and we're all here to have a good time.  If the inevitable happens and one side or the other needs a res, or accidentally trains the other side, remember that we're here to help and have fun.  We'll do our best to work things out reasonable without resorting to flames.<br>
<br>
Also note that VC sent a scout group up last night and some of them may, in fact be in hate right now with you guys, hopefully no conflicts have occurred already!  =)<br>
